{"tid":522413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一地兩檢】批大律師公會過火極端　湯家驊：中央有權明日取消基本法","createTime":"2018-01-07T14:06:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T00:25:16.000Z","uid":76310,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"acba0b75901ff3a8bc56ed6b89c1b8da45d63c86","tid":522413,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T14:06:50.000Z","msg":"全國人大常委會去年12月批准《高鐵西九龍站設立口岸實施「一地兩檢」的合作安排》（下稱安排），但大律師公會發聲明質疑法律基礎。行政會議成員湯家驊表示，看到聲明有感慨，指大律師公會以往的聲明用字都較持平、理性、專業及非政客式，但今次的聲明「有違任何正常解讀」的說法過於極端。                                <br />\n湯家驊今早出席商台節目時，開首就強調非為一地兩檢護航，如遇不合理的事就會據理力爭，與是否行會成員無關。他表示，無意與公會對着幹，但認為對方說法忽略終審庭過往審判基本法的基本原則。他又指「法律係技術性的學問」，「無咩人」可以同律師爭論，故此要說出切合討論基本條件的看法。<br />\n湯家驊再次提到，憲法是指導性文件，用於處理基本原則，非細緻的議題，與一般法律不同，要從目的、用意去解讀。他指，香港人對憲法研究可能不着重，「希望香港人多啲就憲法作研究」。湯又指不敢指公會缺乏憲法研究，因為公會不乏有人對憲法有研究，但一地兩檢是敏感、政治性議題：「我係會理解大律師公會點解會發出一個咁嘅聲明。」<br />\n湯家驊指出，一國兩制是由下而上、港府向中央提出，若指「安排是一國兩制最大的倒退」是過火的說法。他直指：「如果北京唔想一國兩制繼續，使唔使咁麻煩，北京政府絕對有權聽日取消基本法。」<br />\n湯家驊提到，據其所屬民主思路的民調，港人對一國兩制沒有增加負面看法，對人權自由保障感到更加樂觀，但國際社會對港法治有負面看法，他指是因為國際社會不了解香港，從負面報道理解香港，才有負面看法。<br />\n湯呼籲港人，無論有沒有法律認識，「可能要出多少少力」，令國際給予公平些的評價。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180107/s00001/13aac65d011a31c5b3657f235335b557.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180107%2Fs00001%2F13aac65d011a31c5b3657f235335b557.jpg&h=6f7c8ca8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"642b006d48bf03c80e6dfc91489969eb017a9fab","tid":522413,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T14:07:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180107/s00001/1515297580683\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180107%2Fs00001%2F1515297580683&d=3vk22WsPN55cX0DBZHDi454%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f85cf93a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180107%2Fs00001%2F1515297580683&h=d56386fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180107/s00001/1515297580683</a>"},{"pid":"6e2d8e59bf88bcb022fb09081ed3451488b286e8","tid":522413,"uid":20856,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T14:50:24.000Z","msg":"快啦屌。"},{"pid":"b8ed30e7bbda24c0fefad1d8a9d0b4ee7e5cced3","tid":522413,"uid":156901,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T14:53:27.000Z","msg":"請即取消，等睇仆街。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ced2ef997fb23491b84fd8568257d2217e8be5","tid":522413,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T14:56:16.000Z","msg":"樂觀SIR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d439243fa4a89a8edb3b4cf7a646eddc45daa09","tid":522413,"uid":1049,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T14:57:42.000Z","msg":"支持取消基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8514abcbc9b55004d6f2eca80c2356a281c64fb","tid":522413,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d439243fa4a89a8edb3b4cf7a646eddc45daa09","tid":522413,"uid":1049,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T14:57:42.000Z","msg":"支持取消基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"睇下點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b0081495faf387804ffa86fc86db332e4dec9d","tid":522413,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T16:16:12.000Z","msg":"壹周刊: 咩係衰十一　湯家驊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/507566/1?ref=android\" dat